msgstr ""
"They bring you the slave and remove his restraints, apparently relieved to "
"get rid of him. \"I wasn't stuck in there with them. They were stuck in "
"there with me.\" says the freshly freed troublesome slave. You "
"diplomatically nod and welcome them aboard."

