msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:937
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN_GOTAWAY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Zoltans escape before you can slaughter them for scrap, and contrary to "
"what you thought, actually do denounce you. Fair enough."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:939
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_GEAR_BUYER_ZOLTAN_GOTAWAY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:950
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find a welcoming, lively senior hermit in a small space station chock-full of civilian and military supplies, apparently all for herself. \n"
"\t\t\"Hello foreigner, I know all about this sector, care to listen and have some tea?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:953
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Stay for a while. This could be helpful."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:955
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Name's Bruntilda. As you've certainly noticed, this sector is occupied by "
"three main subfactions, and they all have their own personality!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:957
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Politely interrupt and ask where those supplies came from."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:959
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Oh, aren't you curious! You see my dear, my sons work in this sector in "
"\"management\" and \"marketing\" positions. At one point they realized they "
"didn't have the time or patience to assess newcomers and teach them our "
"ways. So they came up with this gig for their sweet ol' mama, and they're "
"always making sure I am cared for.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:961
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "I see. Nice to meet you."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:963
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Now that you can guess why nobody's pillaged the place yet, there are things"
" you could learn about. \"What else would you like to know, dear?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:965
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Think of some questions."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:976
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "We don't have time to waste with some grandma's \"intel\"."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:978
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You say goodbye, gaining and losing nothing, which isn't that bad when you "
"think about it."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:981
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:985
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:998
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/text"
msgstr "Ask her..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1001
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "... about the Gatekeepers."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1003
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"This is supposed to be a bit of a surprise, but I've met some charming lads and lassies who never made it out of the sector because they didn't know. So I'll tell you: you're not leaving the sector without a fight (unless you're transporting one of our friends, hah!). Steer clear until you're prepared.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tThe Bam gatekeeper will be a tough nut to crack, but any missile defense and sufficient shielding should keep you safe.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\tThe Punk gatekeeper has a bit of a chaotic mess going on, but it's mostly ion and anti-bio damage you must watch out for.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\tThe Scorch gatekeeper will have you on fire soon and repeatedly, and that won't work too well against it either. But surely you already figured that one out!\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tJust don't let my sons know i told you all that, Heeeheeehee! Oh and you can always just run away if you're a pussycat...\"\n"
"\t\t\t\tYou can tell that even she would no longer respect you if you did that, but you must also think about the reality you're trying to save."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1016
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask her something else."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1020
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1022
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You grab your things."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1024
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1032
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "... about the subfaction names."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1034
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"What kind of names are those? RadiKal Bam? Punk? Scorch? Is it from a kid's show or something?\" you ask.\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\"Not much to it really. Since so many people have been calling them radicals from the beginning of this little operation, my sons and their little friends simply embraced it. The subfactions just needed a little extra to tell themselves apart, and people don't really like talking too much around here. So they kept it short and to the point. Also I've heard something about variables? I'm the exception, chatting is so enjoyable!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1040
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask her something else."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1044
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1046
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You grab your things."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1048
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1056
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "... about the RK equipment design philosophy."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1058
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Maybe you're just a little slow in the head, so just in case, let me lay it out for youuu.\" You repress the urge to respond to the insult.\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\"Members of Bam believe in the blunt efficiency of impactful, stunning hits or events. Such as a good bonk to the dome, like i taught my children!\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tThe Punk prefer technological superiority, counter-intelligence and all that jazz. They tend to bring less firepower and more fancy gadgets to the table.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tLastly the Scorch just want to watch things burn, and have ways to make sure they do. Some jealous foreigners like to spout nonsense about pacts with otherwordly creatures, especially among the Scorch. Isn't it sad, how low people will go?\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tI hope that clears it up for y'all youngsters!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1069
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask her something else."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1073
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1075
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You grab your things."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1077
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1085
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "... about the prices."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1087
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"It takes a lot of specialized equipment to discreetly get so many crafting"
" materials into a hidden sector, or so my sons told me. That leads to high "
"prices, but not so much for the local production of course!\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1090
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask her something else."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1094
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Leave."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1096
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "You grab your things."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1098
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1129
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "Threaten her for the supplies!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1131
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Emboldened by her physical frailty, you decide chatting is never gonna be as"
" useful as just taking what you want."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1133
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "How about you just shut up and give us all of those suppl-"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1135
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you can finish your despicable threat, you feel the cold dagger belonging to a cloaked security drone pressing on your neck, and realize this whole place is obviously heavily defended.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\"Uneducated scallywags, eh? Another disappointment, but it is clear that our little business is attractive to this type of people. What a waste of good tea. Out with you now.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1139
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Wait a sec! You won't believe it but, this really isn't who we are..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1141
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[5]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You shamefully \"offer\" some supplies as an apology, find out why the pile is so big, and tell your crew in very clear terms that this event is not to be talked about ever again.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\tYou also feel like even though this happened in this hidden sector, word of your lack of morals could somehow reach the outside world."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1159
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_INTEL_REAL\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "Alright, we'll be on our way now. Thank you for the tea."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1164
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_GOODBYE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"She looks cheerful. \"Why, thank you! Very few of you young'uns take a pause to listen to an old lady around these parts. For some reason they seem to favor... 'enhanced interrogation' I think the kids call it? Something about manufacturing details. Anyhoo, farewell!\"\n"
"\tYou notice a shuttle sent to share a little of her supplies with you. That job might be lonelier than it looks, and you wonder how often her sons visit her."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1170
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RADIKAL_PHILO_GOODBYE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1183
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you get here, you notice that you're surrounded by a small Zoltan fleet intercepting every ship passing through here. An urgent hail from a heavily armed Zoltan Elite comes through. \n"
"\tNeedless to say, it would look suspicious not to take the hail.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t[Developer note: This buggy quest will be reworked soon. Consider it a forced fight, or engage with it knowing the risks.]"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1191
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Answer it."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1193
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"As you may know if you're not a brainless savage, this sector has been providing armament to the Duskbringers. We have recently started tackling this problem.\n"
"\t\t\tLike any vessel in transit in a lawless armament-manufacturing area like this one, you will be subjected to the mandatory thorough search for said armament. The fight against illegal weapon proliferation starts with you. Do not resist.\"\n"
"\t\t\tZoltans consider this area a very serious issue. If they find any RadiKal equipment, it may be confiscated, or you might be fined based on how many you're carrying."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1200
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"zoltan_peacekeeper\"]/text"
msgstr "(Zoltan Peacekeeper) We were sent to help you."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1202
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"zoltan_peacekeeper\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"At last, the reinforcements. Here is your warrant. You'll find criminals in this sector, usually hiding in hazardous beacons. Seize their illegal gear and drop it off at the station. The coordinates are on the back.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tIt's safe to assume that not every \"criminal\" will relinquish their RK gear without a fight, but this could greatly benefit your mission."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1210
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"zoltan_peacekeeper\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1214
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"zoltan_peacekeeper\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1221
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"human_soldier\"]/text"
msgstr "(Human Soldier) We were sent to help you."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1223
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"human_soldier\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"At last, the reinforcements. Here is your warrant. You'll find criminals in this sector, usually hiding in hazardous beacons. Seize their illegal gear and drop it off at the station. The coordinates are on the back.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tIt's safe to assume that not every \"criminal\" will relinquish their RK gear without a fight, but this could greatly benefit your mission."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1231
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"human_soldier\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1235
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"human_soldier\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1242
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Agree to the search."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1247
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Ask what happens if you refuse."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1249
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Thanks to the merciful recent amendment 3473-B delta, captains may choose to participate in the funding of control vessels like this one, and report to the closest Zoltan police station within 12 jump cycles instead of immediately submitting to the search.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tEven though you have no intention of taking that detour, they would leave you alone for now."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1254
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Pay up."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1256
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You begrudgingly transfer the scrap but manage to fake a smile, taking "
"comfort in the fact that your equipment's safe... at least for now."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1264
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Agree to the search."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1273
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Try to ignore it and just pass through. [Recommended]"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1275
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"You admission of guilt in facilitating terrorist operations has been recorded and filed for the trial of any surviving spouse(s) and/or heir(s). You will not escape the law.\"\n"
"\t\t\tSounds like you'll have to fight your way through. In fact you wonder how you managed to convince yourself this could end any differently."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1281
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1304
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/text"
msgstr "They come aboard and search your ship..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1307
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1309
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Luckily you had nothing to worry about, and after leaving your ship, without"
" a word the Zoltans immediately cut comms to focus on a different ship. You "
"wonder what could have happened. In any case this took a while, too long to "
"do anything special on your ship."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1311
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1318
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1320
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before long, they do find something. \"Understand that without justification"
" for this, which you may still provide, we will apply the necessary "
"sanctions, which may be a fine or outright confiscation of the offending "
"equipment. Both may be avoided if you willingly leave someone with us for "
"interrogation.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1322
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_ACCEPT\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_HAS_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1330
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Maybe you forgot you were carrying RadiKal gear, or maybe you just didn't "
"find a way to avoid the search. Regardless, they are now fining you for each"
" piece!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1332
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "Let them calculate your total fine."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1334
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"One illegal piece of gear, take this minimal fine as a warning. If you had"
" any more \"RadiKal\" gear than that, we would have been forced to direct "
"you to the local Police Station for processing.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1344
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"2\"]/text"
msgstr "Let them calculate your total fine."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1346
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"2\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Two illegal pieces of gear. You should really know better than to give up ethics for power.\"\n"
"\t\t\tSupposedly you can get some of your scrap back by surrendering your illegal gear at the Police Station, but somehow you doubt that. It might be worth it to pay them a visit regardless."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1357
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/text"
msgstr "Let them calculate your total fine."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1359
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Three illegal pieces of gear... The federation really hires any random scum these days. We will be notifying your leadership.\"\n"
"\t\t\tSupposedly you can get some of your scrap back by surrendering your illegal gear at the Police Station, but somehow you doubt that. It might be worth it to pay them a visit regardless."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1371
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/text"
msgstr "Let them calculate your total fine."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1373
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"DJMOD_SUM_RADIKAL_GEAR\""
" and @lvl=\"4\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"FOUR or more illegal pieces of gear! What th-... I do not even wish to know. What a horrible person you must be. Luckily for you, this is the maximum fine stipulated in the applicable regulation. I suppose nobody foresaw that anyone would make themselves any more of a wretched menace to society than that.\"\n"
"\t\t\tSupposedly you can get some of your scrap back by surrendering your illegal gear at the Police Station, but somehow you doubt that. It might be worth it to pay them a visit regardless."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1385
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CHECK_ANY_CREW\"]/text"
msgstr "Give someone up for interrogation instead."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1390
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "Surprise headshot that nosy lightbulb. (Risky)"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1392
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Quickly but accurately aiming through the hardlight, you splatter the chief inspector with your blaster, right before taking cover for the explosion! \n"
"\t\t\tVery satisfying ... but can you deal with the rest of them?"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1398
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICECHECK_RK_FINED\"]/choice[6]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Pop them all!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1406
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_INTERROGATED_CREW\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You come to an agreement where they keep one of your crew in custody so they"
" can explain what you were doing in this sector. It's a lengthy process, you"
" will certainly finish your mission (or die) before you see them again."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1409
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_INTERROGATED_CREW\"]/removeCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Your crew cannot be cloned as they are not dead, though they might go insane"
" shortly."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1413
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_INTERROGATED_CREW\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1431
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr ""
"Where Zoltan Police holds confiscated RadiKal gear and seized supplies."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1433
msgid "data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You wonder how exactly the Zoltans set up a fortified police station in such an area undeterred, but it is proof of their determination.\n"
"\t\"Welcome captain. Since you found this place, you must be part of the special Federation corps attached to this regulation effort.\" Might be far from the truth, but you decide to roll with it.\n"
"\t\"What can we do for you?\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1442
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Request supplies."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1444
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"We have seized quite a lot of supplies from this band of criminals, at "
"great cost. But you are our ally in this operation, so help yourself. Within"
" the limits of the Alliance Supply and Logistics Act of course.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1450
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Request RadiKal gear."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1452
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"After some brief icebreaker chitchat which the officer seems to midly enjoy, you take your shot asking for a free piece. What passes for his facial expression changes that instant. \n"
"\t\t\t\t\"Surely you must be confused. This is labeled and sorted trial evidence, in the form of illegal weaponry which is unsafe for use, unethical and generally a threat to law and order. Thanks for stopping by, I have work to do now.\""

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1457
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Feign surprise."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1459
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You expected this. \"Oh? We weren't informed. Sorry for asking, keep up the good work.\" \n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Zoltan throws you one suspicious look, but he's too busy dealing with the paperwork to investigate, and you're out without a hitch, but with nothing to show for it."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1464
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Meh."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1471
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Hint that you can do this the hard way instead..."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1473
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Now certain that you're not, in fact, here to help at all, the Zoltan rings "
"the alarm and you rush back to your ship. The fight is breaking out within "
"range of the station's defense turrets!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1484
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"The police station breaks apart, its confiscated illegal contents and "
"extensive array of administrative backups reduced to mere scrap for you to "
"take."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1488
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Having killed the crew, you manage to snatch some supplies and a labeled "
"crate before the turrets tear your ship apart."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1491
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "Open it."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:1493
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_ZOLTAN_POLICESTATION_RK\"]/deadCrew/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
